uses
  Messages, Forms, SysUtils, StrUtils, Variants, Classes, Controls, Graphics, Contnrs,
  LCLintf, LCLType,
  Dialogs, EditorOptions, SynEditHighlighter, SynEditSearch, SynEdit,
